Opera Mini for iPhone已经正式<a href="http://my.opera.com/community/countup/">递交到</a>iPhone App store，<a href="http://apple.slashdot.org/story/10/03/23/1946223/Opera-Mini-For-iPhone-Submitted-To-App-Store-Today">交给苹果审核</a>。<i>
