➜用谷歌搜南方*末
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=16929	40680
Walled 写道 "偶然用Google搜了一下某报纸的网站：<i>
<a href="http://www.google.com/search?sourceid=navclient&amp;aq=0h&amp;oq=&amp;hl=zh-CN&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;rlz=1T4CULB_zh-CN___CN359&amp;q=%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB">南方周末</a> ：无法显示网页<br>
